Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.71,0:04:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.41,0:04:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你破坏了原著的形象
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.58,0:04:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕的现实呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.81,0:04:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要也是按照原著来拍
