Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.90,0:04:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下 导演
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.73,0:04:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有想借原著之路逃跑的导演来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.44,0:04:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真烦 按原著来拍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.04,0:04:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是按原著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.23,0:04:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个偶像就必须要拍那种脱衣戏了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.61,0:04:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 那样不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.24,0:04:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为都和原著一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.93,0:04:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.61,0:04:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导演
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.00,0:04:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:04:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔也有无法依照原著的时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.19,0:05:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是难懂的事呢
